OL,5, An NHS trust has been accused of adding
OL,6, to the records of a man the day after  
OL,7, he took his own life to "correct their 
OL,8, mistakes".                             
OL,10,FCharles Ndhlovu, 33, died under the    
OL,11,Fcare of Cambridgeshire and Peterborough
OL,12,FNHS Foundation Trust (CPFT) in 2017.   
OL,14,FHis mother, Angelina Pattison, said the
OL,15,Fway her son's case had been handled had
OL,16,F"upset me so much".                    
OL,18,FThe trust did not respond to the claim 
OL,19,Fabout the records being added to but   
OL,20,Fsaid learning from deaths was "vital". 
